quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"He innde Allah jurumdeero jormotoo…óo oo"
  1,2,"Denndaangal jettoo…óe ngoodanii joom binnde."
  1,3,"Jurumdeero jurmotoo…óo"
  1,4,"Jey…óo √±alngu njo…ìdi"
  1,5,"Ko Aan tan min ndewata te ko Aan tan min mballintoo."
  1,6,"Feewnu min e laawol pooctingol"
  1,7,"Laawol …ìeen …ìe neemin-…óaa …ìe ngonaa tikkanaa…ìe te …ìe majjaani."
